55:07.554 --> 55:10.347
Promise me you'll never tell. Promise.

55:10.390 --> 55:12.808
- I promise.
- Never!

55:12.892 --> 55:14.727
They don't understand.

55:14.811 --> 55:16.729
They can't understand.

55:22.277 --> 55:23.902
What's that sound?

