56:09.491 --> 56:11.909
Jerry, finish it, please.

56:13.370 --> 56:15.329
Please!

56:17.874 --> 56:21.085
Jerry, finish it, please!

56:30.470 --> 56:31.637
Jerry.

56:34.724 --> 56:35.849
What is it?

56:39.938 --> 56:43.148
My mama died up in that room.

56:50.490 --> 56:52.616
- Sorry, I'm sorry.
