01:03:12.497 --> 01:03:14.289
- Jerry, you're a serial killer!
- Sheriff Weinbacher.

01:03:14.373 --> 01:03:15.540
No, he isn't.

01:03:15.666 --> 01:03:17.375
Now with the aid of the FBI,
we have developed

01:03:17.418 --> 01:03:19.920
